    "en": {
      "title": "Don't visit Sri Lanka unless essential",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Britain and New Zealand have advised their nationals to avoid traveling to Sri Lanka except for essential matters.",
        "A travel advisory to Sri Lanka has been updated yesterday (05) to avoid travel.",
        "In Sri Lanka, which is facing a severe economic crisis, there is a shortage of essential commodities including medicine, gas, fuel and food.",
        "The British Foreign and Commonwealth Office and the New Zealand Embassy in Sri Lanka have informed their citizens that the shortage of petrol and diesel has severely affected business, emergency and transport services.",
        "Roadblocks, protests and demonstrations are likely to happen in a very short period of time, the travel advisories issued by the countries said."
      ],
